				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\lambda _{u}$$\end{document}λu (Hiorns et al. 2014; Hill et al. 2012; Robertson et al. 2011; Holzapfel and Ogden 2010). The strain energy functions for each of the constituents are given in Online Resource 1.2.

